title: Attach by Architecture
description:
Total Switching (TAO) by Business Entity (BE). Rules:

Service value of all product that was shipped in the current and last 11 months (12 total) with an uncovered status that are not past or approaching LDoS (in the next 12 months). Price Assumption - 50.2% discount taken off of SNTC NBD (Default Service List Price).
